OL,8,FNews Wales Reporter Rhys Williams has
OL,9,Fthe latest
OL,11,FThere may be more than a thousand
OL,12,Fportraits, but each tells its own
OL,13,Fstory.
OL,15,FMore than a decade ago, Grahame Hurd-
OL,16,FWood embarked on a mammoth task. To
OL,17,Fpaint the portrait of every resident
OL,18,Fof his city. Thankfully, he lives in
OL,19,Fthe UK's smallest, St Davids in
OL,20,FPembrokeshire.
