OL,3,CArtist attempts to paint the portrait
OL,4,Cof all 1,800 people of city
OL,6,FIt all started when his fiancee
OL,7,FDebbie, who had cancer, asked him to
OL,8,Fpaint her portrait.
OL,10,F"Unfortunately she died quite
OL,11,Fquickly......so I completed her
OL,12,Fportrait after her passing...and it
OL,13,Fwas very powerful for me and I
OL,14,Fthought, this is what I really want to
OL,15,Fdo."
