OL,6,FSince that tragedy Grahame has been
OL,7,Fsitting down with his fellow St
OL,8,FDavid's residents, often for hours on
OL,9,Fend, to listen to their stories and
OL,10,Fcapture their characters. We visited
OL,11,Fhim two years ago after he reached the
OL,12,Fmilestone of a thousand portraits.
OL,14,FNow his ever expanding collection can
OL,15,Fbe seen in an exhibition at the
OL,16,FPierhead Futures Gallery in Cardiff
OL,17,FBay.
