OL,6,FThe target may be the 1,800 residents
OL,7,Fof St David's, but Grahame doesn't
OL,8,Fexpect the project to ever stop. Nor
OL,9,Fdoes he want it to.
OL,11,F"As long as I'm holding my brush...I'm
OL,12,Fgoing to carry on doing it."
